originalText.text: They're very friendly here. I was nervous leaving my first child here, as any parent would when they first drop their kid off, but they're great. My son is making friends with the other kids there and he gets excited to see the staff that work there. I feel lucky to have found a place where I don't feel any hesitation after I drop my son off in the morning.

originalText.text: My 11 month old son has been going to Young Unlimited Child Care since he was 5 months old.  We toured a ton of daycares before choosing this one and I am so glad we did.  It truly feels like a family.  The children get along so well with one another and my son is always excited to see the staff.
